Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?! A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Slaying of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:43.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Smells awful!\N- What's all this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:47.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got that?\NSend them this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:51.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like we're getting\nrid of insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, are you about ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this one of\nthe demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:00.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's nose is\nawfully sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How beautiful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Miroku!\NWhere're you goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:12.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming!\NGet back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!\NIt's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, do you still\nfeel sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:38.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWhere's Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He went after\nsome strange woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:44.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?! While we\nwere working?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was awfully pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:50.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He probably went and asked her\nto have his baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!\NA b-baby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:58.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... so you are the princess\nof a very prominent clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But my clan was ruined\nby war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:04.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I am the last survivor\nof my House.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to restore my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish to bear the child\nof a strong lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you sought me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such fine taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you heed my request?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:28.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought it was too good\nto be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Giant mantis...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,disguised as a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I devoured the insides\nof the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You picked the wrong victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! My Wind Tunnel\ngot nicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know if\NI'm imagining it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but the girls have been\nlooking at me quite coldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:27.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't you just go to\npick up a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:31.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why they think\nyou're a lecher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You may not believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- We don't.\N- You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish you'd hear me out\nat least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shucks... It still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:01.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That praying mantis made\nmy Wind Tunnel bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:08.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not go! Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me go, Master Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:17.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will be sucked into your\nfather's Wind Tunnel, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:24.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He went out before dawn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, the monk said that\nhe was going on a journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and to wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:40.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Miroku! Always acting\non his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:46.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My father got sucked into\nhis own Wind Tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and disappeared without\nleaving a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In time, I probably will\nend up dying like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what's this giant hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:11.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my father's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:21.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin, are you there?\NIt's Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:25.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes... drunk as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You drunken monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:34.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Miroku.\NSo you're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin, if you keep\ndrinking to excess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you won't live long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you come here\nto lecture me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... A demon nicked\nmy Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you repair it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will die tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:07:00.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not! Just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to be\nsucked in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:09.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, now...\NCalm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll stitch it up, but\NI must warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:16.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until the wound is\ncompletely healed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you cannot expose\nyour Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Wind Tunnel will spread\nfrom the nicks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and hasten your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:29.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will no longer be able\nto help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:34.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will get my medicinal herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:37.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go and thoroughly purify\nyour dirty self.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:43.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... So that Master Mushin is\nthe one who raised you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:47.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... Everything bad,\NI learned from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:51.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He acts gruff, but he seems\nvery kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:53.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:58.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Miroku... Going timid\nover little nicks like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I can't blame him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's had such a tragic life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:07.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did Miroku leave us\nlike that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it 'cuz you treated him\nso coldly yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:11.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:16.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! As if he's so sensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Master Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga? You're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:21.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, I returned last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the monk was\nacting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:32.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He kept staring at his right hand\nand seemed deep in thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what he\nwas thinking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, let's find Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... but we're not\nsure what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Find him? But how!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave 'im alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Finding the Sacred Jewel\nfragments is more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku...what happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:05.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's still day, but unusually dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you take your medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:26.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel quite groggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.\NFrankly, I don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:47.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Difficult you're not.\NI'll put you at ease soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:53.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's toxic insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This time, it's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he's keeping us\nunder surveillance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,something must've happened\nto Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm following it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Okay!\N- Hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:32.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... are you still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-who... are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:39.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In exchange for a fragment of\nthe Sacred Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I promised Naraku to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm the Demon Worm Charmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The medicine has numbed\nyour body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:01.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and save yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look well... the demons\nare gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you stay with me,\nyou'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:41.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:45.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can ward them off until\nthe medicine wears off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,B-but!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:49.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:00.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He talked big, bu\nno way he can handle it alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha must be close by!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is our only clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't lose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! More insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fool around with a woman\nand have to pay with my life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such is my fate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is in danger,\nafter all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He can't use his\NWind Tunnel right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:57.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His Wind Tunnel got nicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before the monk became weird\nhe was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,if Miroku used his Wind Tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:07.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the nicks would allow\nthe hole to spread wider...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:11.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,shortening his life,\nwhich is already short.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's the temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:20.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go right through 'em all, Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... ain't... gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,waste my time here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:45.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you want to eat me,\ngo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unlike someone else,\NI accept death with grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't go fighting,\nlike Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:16.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is where you've\nbeen hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha... you've come for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:26.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:27.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:28.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:31.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Idiot! Why did you disappear\nwithout a word?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:34.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We worried so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're okay, Monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...they are all here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said everything\NI meant to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:50.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:55.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall punish anyone who\ndisturbs the peace of my temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the monk called Mushin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:01.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Interesting... fight me if you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:06.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... please...\ndon't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:12.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good boy! After all, I am the\none who raised Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:17.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, you old monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga's transformation\nwas thwarted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:36.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Feisty boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:47.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:52.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are bound by my special magic,\nyet you can still move?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I wonder how long\nyou can last?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what's that... coming out\nof the monk's mouth!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon Worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The monk is controlled by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't he be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:12.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There must be\na Demon Worm Charmer nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Find him and take the pot away\nand aim it at the monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:18.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Demon Worm will leave him\nand return to the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:23.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.\NLet's search, Old Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons aren't decreasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's in danger too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, I'm glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:37.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Feel safer over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no mistake!\NThat's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- He got away!\N- Let's go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}These sutra beads are draining\nmy strength...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:04.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm starting to feel weak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:16.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You no longer have the power\nto fight back the swarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you wish to be\ndevoured alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:23.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall be benevolent and\nchop off your head first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:27.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those are scum demons\nthat have no taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:30.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Scum demons devour\nonly scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get your hopes too high,\nstinkin' monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only I can cure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:41.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the only one who can\nrepair Miroku's Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:46.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Left as is, he might all be\nsucked into it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Resign yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone in this temple\nwill soon die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:05.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:07.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hachi... prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You and I will probably be\nsucked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rather than be eaten the\ntheir likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this is much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes sir! I'll follow you,\NMaster Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hachi! Support me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:43.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He'll suck in the\NSacred Jewel fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:44.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's losing strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't hold my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:10.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inu... yasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it! If you try to open\nyour Wind Tunnel again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll break this arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can die if you wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:26.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But don't die so easily\nwhen you're with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Feeling guilty of\nabandoning you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,isn't something I'll enjoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:36.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...waking up to\nin the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:48.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons have all been...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:08.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The true power of the Tetsusaiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,for the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's taking so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:40.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He has to stitch the wound.\NIt takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool... being so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk! How is Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there... Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:51.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Monk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:59.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope you did a good job\nstitching up the Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:05.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I did what I could, but the\NWind Tunnel had spread further.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean\nhis life is shortened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How much longer\ndoes he have?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:13.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku's Wind Tunnel was created...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:16.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,by a curse placed upon\nhim by Naraku the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:19.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hence, if Naraku is destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:22.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the curse is lifted\nand Miroku's life will be spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:26.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sooner you get him, the better.\NThat is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's very strong-willed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:33.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can he always\nbe so cheerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:34.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:36.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure that actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he worries about each\nand every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:42.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh? He's awake!\N- Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:46.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll be all right.\NThe monk stitched the Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anything wrong with your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:04.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Committing sexual harrassment\neven now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:07.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He ain't gonna die for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:10.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Miroku blood\nis to be feared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:50.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango had a younger brother,\NKohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:53.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He passed away\nwhen he was caught in Naraku's plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:58.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so sad to hear that the scar\non her back is a reminder of her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:02.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is attacked by a chain scythe!\NSango gets tense!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:05.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could the boy who throws\nthe chain scythe be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:07.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But... How?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:11.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Sango's Suffering and Kohaku's Life".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.21,0:24:13.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
